{
  "stem": "2460.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they went to lay flowers on the tomb of the unknown soldier.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we are children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We ran after the car.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We wanted to see, with my Gentile friends and Jewish friends.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at the tomb of the unknown soldier, they were yelling those anti-Jewish slogans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I just left my friends, and I ran home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was crying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I told my father, my mother what did they-- what I heard.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the father tried to quiet the things down, that it's-- it's just some people that it doesn't have too much importance.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it really, the things went OK for the first couple months.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the difference was tremendous after the Czechoslovakians left.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wanted to ask you, do you think your father told you it wouldn't make a big difference because he wanted to comfort you--",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--a child that was--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--you know, obviously--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he was just trying to comfort us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He saw the-- the disaster.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we know very little.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The truth is, we know very little.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because from the beginning, the first couple years were fairly OK.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in 1941, when they started the anti-Jewish laws, then our radios were taken away, and the news was pro-German, although the Hungarians directly did not attack the Jews.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the-- the children couldn't go to the gymnasiums.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The-- all the-- the children couldn't go to study doctors and lawyers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So slowly, slowly, we adopted to this different and antisemitic life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Gentile population, they adapted also.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Slowly, slowly they became anti-- antisemites.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Most of them, if not all of them, but most of them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they adapted in a negative way?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Negative way.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The teachers especially.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
